data.description: Charming, north side home awaits new owners to love it as much as this family has! Many memories have been made in this 3 BR 2 BA home. A welcoming entry, open living area, dining room & updated kitchen. Cozy fireplace is perfect for fall & winter evenings! Located on a quaint & quiet street, the home shows off a well-maintained outdoor space. Laugh with neighbors or enjoy coffee on the welcoming front porch. Relax in the evening under the outdoor patio area or gather around the fire pit! Create memories & traditions at the famous Green Acres- just down the street! Newer metal roof & some windows, gutters, updated plumbing & garage door in 2022 as well as updates to well in 2023...peace of mind for years to come!
